{"tid":2385935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「零」加特脫「魔」投舊主莫天才","createTime":"2021-01-29T09:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T09:43:21.000Z","uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a052f71de169dc8c6530cfb0b55d232384603efa","tid":2385935,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】曾在年前錄得0入球及0助攻的曼聯中場連加特，將會被外借由前帥莫耶斯領軍的韋斯咸至季尾。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯中場連加特（Jesse Lingard）看來很快就能逃出奧脫福，根據《每日郵報》報道，曼聯和韋斯咸經過一輪艱難談判後，終於達成借用協議，他將以150萬費用效力韋斯咸至季尾，對方將支付8萬英鎊周薪。<br />\n<br />\n連加特近年水準急速下滑，上次入波要追溯至2019年11月28日的歐霸盃賽事，而曾於2019年整年英超都沒入球及助攻，淪為球迷笑柄，在本港有球迷以「零格」稱之，今季更遭蘇斯克查棄用，至今僅在盃賽上陣3次。<br />\n<br />\n現任韋斯咸領隊莫耶斯在2013/14年曾執教曼聯，在季前賽領軍的首個入球，就由連加特射入，不過兩人合作時間不長，連加特該季先後被外借至伯明翰和白禮頓，如今在另一球會再續前緣。"},{"pid":"59b2d4b67e09f3c9e78ecab223df7003a9660fe6","tid":2385935,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c513bc914aeb344929318e0e0442653d8876c5ce","tid":2385935,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:40:24.000Z","msg":"死廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171ed9bbf6553acef3b25098f6fcbe0ee1dfeb13","tid":2385935,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:42:43.000Z","msg":"sor 開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac94d4580425343503373f0a5761da2be86a3395","tid":2385935,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:43:21.000Z","msg":"返波台啦"}]}